      "content": "Wait, \"standard procedure\"? An adjustment of that size should have been flagged in the site change orders and approved by my office before the pour. I don't see any utility issue noted in the pre-pour survey. If you modified the footprint without authorization, that's a huge violation. Are you sure there wasn't a measurement error during the pour itself?",
